admin create a feature table to list all the features present in our app
license type , mentions all the features that are enabled in the plan,
api takes all the feature from feature table and mark it as disable.
api first check the feature mentioned by admin exist or not in db, if exist mark it as enable,
now the plan is created

user when enters create a license , by hitting create license / type where he mention the type of license he want
api creates a license for it {
license_id,license_type,expiry_date
} and return a license id, and internally it maps to the license type he requested,

next time when the app requires which features are enable in this license , it just sends a license_id, api checks its expiry date first, if it is valid, find the license type it is mapped to ,and send the features enabled as true or false in that license

user will give first time only {
vin,
license type he wants,
type of vehicle,
expiry data,
}
and in return he gets a license id so he do not need to send all details everytime,except during update of license
when he gives license id next time{
he gets features enabled based on its license type and type of vehicle
}
